    <description>
		This is a modification of Portable.Ninject (https://github.com/onovotny/ninject/) which is compiled in PCL 111 profile and based on v3.3.1.
		It means that this library can be used both in PCL and .NET Standard libraries (which is not possible when using original Portable.Ninject). 
		Supported platforms: iOS, Android, UWP
    </description>
    <summary>IoC container for .NET</summary>
    <releaseNotes>Small improvements</releaseNotes>
    <tags>Ninject ioc di portable pcl xamarin ios android monotouch monoandroid uwp</tags>
